Goldsmiths Owner Aurum Up for 200 Million-Pound Sale, Times Says

-- B y   C a r o l i n e   A l e x a n d e r
-- 
2011-04-03T09:10:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-03/goldsmiths-owner-aurum-up-for-200-million-pound-sale-times-says.html
Aurum Holdings Ltd., the company
that owns Goldsmiths, Mappin & Webb and Watches of  Switzerland ,
is up for sale for about 200 million pounds ($322.2 million),
the  Times of London  reported today.  Cavendish Corporate Finance is handling the sale of the
165-store business, according to the report. Aurum Holdings is
controlled by the resolution committee of Landsbanki Islands hf,
it said. 